inscription_text: Peggy Greer|Born 31st March 1815|Died 7th February 1880|To be with Christ|which is far better|Alfred Greer|Born 14th June 1839|Died 9th September 1907|Rejoicing in hope|Patient in tribulation|Alfred Greer S.P.|Born 2nd September 1805|Died 29th December 1891|Yea Lord|Thou knowest that I love thee|Macgregor Greer|Late Captain Royal Engineers|Born 16th July 1844|Died 20th January 1903|I believe that Jesus Christ|is the Son of God
